            <title><![CDATA[“留学哈工大”品牌系列学生活动——【Hi-Topic】校友面对面第二期活动预告]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[“留学哈工大”品牌系列学生活动——【Hi-Topic】校友面对面第二期活动预告]]></description>
            <link>https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/27/121247</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/27/121247</guid>
            <pubDate>Sun, 27 Apr 2025 03:25:40 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded>&lt;section data-pm-slice=&quot;3 3 [&amp;quot;para&amp;quot;,{&amp;quot;tagName&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;section&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;attributes&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;style&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&amp;quot;},&amp;quot;namespaceURI&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&amp;quot;}]&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;【Hi-Topic】校友面对面活动是国际教育学院在“留学哈工大”品牌系列下精心打造的校友深度交流平台。该活动以留学经验分享为核心，致力于打造国际化人才培育范式。为实现这一目标，本平台立足全球胜任力培养，通过构建 “过来人 - 在读生” 实效对话机制，使校友与在校学生之间的交流更具实效性，助力在校学生更好进行学业规划和个人发展。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;The &quot;Alumni Face-to-Face&quot; event is a carefully crafted alumni deep exchange platform under the &quot;Studying at Harbin Institute of Technology&quot; brand series by the College of International Education. Focusing on the sharing of study abroad experiences, this event is dedicated to creating a paradigm for cultivating international talents. To achieve this goal, the platform is based on the cultivation of global competencies, building an effective dialogue mechanism between &quot;alumni and current students&quot; to make the exchange between alumni and current students more effective, helping current students better plan their studies and personal development.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;一、活动主题&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Event Theme&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;section data-pm-slice=&quot;3 3 [&amp;quot;para&amp;quot;,{&amp;quot;tagName&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;section&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;attributes&amp;quot;:{&amp;quot;style&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&amp;quot;},&amp;quot;namespaceURI&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&amp;quot;}]&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;解锁留学密码&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;畅听校友征途&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;Unlock the Code of Studying Abroad&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Listen to the Journey of Alumni&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;二、活动内容&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Event Content&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;本次【Hi-Topic】校友面对面活动邀请到两位即将毕业的优秀毕业生校友亲临现场。首先校友们会进行详细的自我介绍，分享成长历程中的关键节点。随后，校友们将传授学习规划、语言备考、科研竞赛等实用技巧，还会分享时间管理、跨文化适应、心理调适等方面的成长感悟。最后，校友们将送上对学弟学妹的暖心毕业寄语。在整个过程中，同学们可以积极互动，提出自己在留学哈工大相关方面的疑问，与校友深入交流。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;This &quot;Alumni Face-to-Face&quot; event invites two outstanding graduating alumni to attend the event in person. First, the alumni will introduce themselves in detail and share key moments in their growth journeys. Subsequently, they will impart practical skills in study planning, language preparation, scientific research competitions, etc., and also share insights on time management, cross-cultural adaptation, psychological adjustment, and other aspects of growth. Finally, the alumni will offer warm graduation messages to their juniors. Throughout the process, students can actively interact, ask questions about studying at Harbin Institute of Technology, and have in-depth exchanges with the alumni.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;三、活动时间&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Event Time&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;2025年4月29日 17:30-18:30&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;四、活动地点&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Event Location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;正心楼708&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;五、特邀嘉宾简介&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;I&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ntroduction to the Special Guests&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;（一）嘉宾一​&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Guest One&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;毛如意（Maotheng Badatthida)，来自柬埔寨，目前就读于哈尔滨工业大学工商管理专业的大四学生。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;在校期间，她不仅专注专业课程学习以提升管理素养，还积极参与学院组织的文化交流与志愿服务活动，有效培养了跨文化沟通能力和团队协作意识。作为【Hi-Touch】助航社团学习部成员，她致力于促进中外学生互动，积极参与学习分享会等活动，助力中外学生互学共进。即将毕业之际，她计划继续攻读相关领域硕士学位以拓展视野、精进专业能力，并期待未来能与更多志同道合者相遇，共同成长。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Maotheng Badatthida, from Cambodia, is currently a senior majoring in Business Administration at Harbin Institute of Technology.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;During her studies, she not only focused on professional course learning to enhance her management literacy but also actively participated in cultural exchanges and volunteer service activities organized by the college, effectively cultivating her cross-cultural communication skills and team collaboration awareness. As a member of the [Hi-Touch] Navigation Club&apos;s Learning Department, she is committed to promoting interaction between Chinese and foreign students, actively participating in learning sharing sessions and other activities, and helping Chinese and foreign students learn from each other and progress together. On the eve of graduation, she plans to pursue a master&apos;s degree in related fields to broaden her horizons and refine her professional skills, and looks forward to meeting more like-minded individuals in the future to grow together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; data-entity-type=&quot;file&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;109504c7-3070-4749-9ae2-40c3978bb1f1&quot; src=&quot;/sites/today1.prod1.dpweb1.hit.edu.cn/files/inline-images/2025/04/27/1_2.jpg&quot; class=&quot;align-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;（二）嘉宾二&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Guest Two&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;孔罗莎（KONG ROZA），来自柬埔寨，目前就读于哈尔滨工业大学工商管理专业的大四学生。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;在本科学习阶段，孔罗莎始终保持卓越的学术表现，凭借优异成绩荣获柬埔寨高中优秀外国新生奖学金，并以专业第一名的成绩完成全部课程。在专注学业的同时，她积极投身校园与社会服务，曾参与学生迎新志愿服务，在暑期汉语教学志愿活动中贡献力量。此外，她深度参与“遇见柬埔寨”活动的策划与执行工作。目前，孔罗莎正积极申请哈尔滨工业大学硕士学位，期望在工商管理领域进一步深耕，持续提升专业研究能力与实践水平。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Kong Roza, from Cambodia, is currently a senior majoring in Business Administration at Harbin Institute of Technology.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;During her undergraduate studies, Kong Roza maintained an excellent academic performance, winning the Outstanding Foreign Freshman Scholarship from a Cambodian high school with her excellent grades, and completed all courses with the highest scores in her major. While focusing on her studies, she actively participated in campus and social services, contributing to student welcome volunteer services and summer Chinese teaching volunteer activities. In addition, she was deeply involved in the planning and execution of the &quot;Meet Cambodia&quot; event. Currently, Kong Roza is actively applying for a master&apos;s degree at Harbin Institute of Technology, hoping to further delve into the field of business administration, continuously improve her professional research capabilities and practical skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; data-entity-type=&quot;file&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;f6ccf4f8-e698-48d1-aba8-59ff03e3d4bd&quot; src=&quot;/sites/today1.prod1.dpweb1.hit.edu.cn/files/inline-images/2025/04/27/2_0.jpg&quot; class=&quot;align-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;text-align-center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;六、报名方式&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Registration Method&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; data-entity-type=&quot;file&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;8f37e6cf-1a59-4d16-af3a-b0467702be9b&quot; src=&quot;/sites/today1.prod1.dpweb1.hit.edu.cn/files/inline-images/2025/04/27/3_0.jpg&quot; class=&quot;align-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;名额有限，同学们快扫描二维码报名吧！报名后请加入微信群。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Spaces are limited, so students should scan the QR code to register quickly! After registration, please join the WeChat group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; data-entity-type=&quot;file&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;978326ba-2f7d-4cda-adef-fdd748824b29&quot; src=&quot;/sites/today1.prod1.dpweb1.hit.edu.cn/files/inline-images/2025/04/27/4_0.jpg&quot; class=&quot;align-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
